summary: Theon Arc Tarot: The Devil Upright: Double-Dealing Deception, Disillusionment, Trickery, Error, Danger, Disgrace...
caption:
Theon Arc Tarot: The Devil
Upright: Double-Dealing Deception, Disillusionment, Trickery, Error, Danger, Disgrace
Reversed: Trifling Mistakes, Deception, Discovered, Negative Advantage

Notes: Some people were interested in using this as a phone background so I’ve posted a “non-card” version too so the card border doesn’t mess with anything if you’d prefer. I feel so much pressure drawing Ramsay since he’s the favorite of most of my friends.

I tried to capture his unchecked, unbridled intensity in this, I hope I did. 

Tarot meaning reference: Labyrynthos

Finished on: September 17th 2018
Media: Digital
